<template>
    <v-snackbar v-model="sbar">{{ stext }}
        <template v-slot:action="{ attrs }">
            <v-btn :color="scolor" text v-bind="attrs" @click="sbar = false">Close</v-btn>
        </template>
    </v-snackbar>
</template> 

<script>
export default {
    props:{
        snackbar:{type:Boolean,required:true,default:false},
        snackbartext:{type:String,required:true,default:"上传成功"},
        snackcolor:{type:String,required:true,default:"green"}
    },
    data(){
        return{
            sbar:Boolean,
            stext:String,
            scolor:String
        }
    },
    watch:{
	snackbar:function(newValue){
		this.sbar=newValue	
    },
    snackbartext:function(newValue){
        this.stext=newValue
    }
}
}
</script>
